tafsir[26]{c,v,t}:
  88,1,"Mbela arii e Ma-aan nelaaɗo-yeewtere ñalngu darngo muuratngu aade e kuli huli mammba?"
  88,2,"Aade en e ñande darnga ko hiitaaɓe wolla malaaɓe, tawi ko hiitaaɓe Geece mum en na koyi na yankanii."
  88,3,"Hoɗe tampiri callale ɗeɓe ndaasirte, e tonngi tonngiraaɗi."
  88,4,"ɗeen geece na naata yiite wulnge ɓe tampaira nguleeki ki."
  88,5,"Hombo yarnee e seewnde nde ndiyam mum satti nguleeki."
  88,6,"ɓe ngalah ñaamdu si wonah darii, ɗum ko ñaamdu ɓurndu bonde e luuɓde e puɗi soɗi njoori ɗi tookete."
  88,7,"ɗi nafatah ñaamoowo ɗi ittatah heege."
  88,8,"Geece malaaɓe e oon ñalawma na neemi na njalbi, sabu neema."
  88,9,"Golle mum lobbe ɗe ɓe ngolli e aduna na mbela, sabu heɓde njobdi golle mum moftanooɗe na cowa."
  88,10,"E nder Aljanna toowuɗo nokku e darja."
  88,11,"A nanatah e aljanna haala meere e bolle puuyɗe, wonah noon nande ko harmi."
  88,12,"Ina e aljanna he ceewle ilooje, ɓe firlitoo heen noɓe welara."
  88,13,"Ina e hembo leece ɓamtaaɗe."
  88,14,"E kaasaaji na kebla ngam yardeede."
  88,15,"Ina e hembo ngaflaaje pawandiraaɗe yogo e dow yogo."
  88,16,"Ina e hembo mbettule buy na werta kala nokku."
  88,17,"Mbele ɓe ndaaraani ndaarannde teskagol no Alla tagiri ngelooba O eeltaniba aade?"
  88,18,"ɓe ndaara kammu hono mbo ɓamtira haa mbo wonti mbildi ndeenaandi, mbo yanatah e dow mum en."
  88,19,"ɓe ndaara pelle hono ɗe ɓamtira ɗe tabitini leydi haa ndi waasa dimmbaade e dow aade en."
  88,20,"ɓe ndaara leydi ndi hono ndi wertira, ndi heblana yimɓe ngam ɓe koɗa heen."
  88,21,"Aan nelaaɗo waaja ɓe, kulɓinaaɓe lepte Alla, aan ko a baajatooɗo, ɗaɓɓaaka e ma si wonah siftinde, hono kawraangal e iimaan ko junngo Alla woni."
  88,22,"A wonah pawaaɗo e mum en haa mbaawnaaɓe goonɗinde."
  88,23,"Kono oon duntiiɗo iimaan, o yeddi Alla e Nelaaɓe Makko."
  88,24,"Alla lepta mbo ñande darnga lepte ɓurɗe mawnude ɗuum woni naatde yiite o saasa toon haa pooma."
  88,25,"Pellet ko e Amen woni ruttorde maɓɓe caggal maayde."
  88,26,"Refti ko Amen tan woni ko golle mum kaasbate, wonah e goɗɗo goo."
